                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://www.itchotels.com/content/dam/itchotels/in/umbrella/global-offers/suite-memories.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Grand Palace">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Grand Palace</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Select City Walk and DLF Emporio. Conveniently located in the heart of South Delhi, accessible to Lodhi Road, Nehru Place, Okhla Industrial Area and Chhatarpur farms.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="roomDetails_btn">Room Details</a>
